---
title: Mustard Pork & Apple with Honey-Roasted Veggies
description: Sweet slices of apple and fresh thyme lend their flavour to the easy pan sauce in this delectable dish. The veggie sides keep up with the easy theme as they’re all roasted – including the green beans! It's a handy and hands-off way to create a tasty accompaniment to a meal you'll want again and again.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b63dd5030006c03627cb805-e2e48332.jpg
